metadata.name: Silent Etude #1/6
metadata.description:
**My work that I have been working on for a long time and combining most of the techniques is with you..**

 This workS of mine came out with the idea of how to combine the techniques used by artists in the world of NFT on a single work. 

## Techniques i use

Gif art + Glitch art + Minimalism + surreal art + photo manipulation art + collage art
